not used that way.

00:10:03.750 --> 00:10:06.870
So we thought, well we should
sing those songs to kind

00:10:06.870 --> 00:10:08.240
of show the richness of the form.

00:10:08.240 --> 00:10:11.730
And then also we've been writing
songs and using them in ways

00:10:11.730 --> 00:10:14.730
