and more pedestrian puroposes

00:10:14.730 --> 00:10:16.030
to show what it should be.

00:10:16.030 --> 00:10:17.330
And it used to be used
for everything.

00:10:17.330 --> 00:10:18.730 position:56%
Because it was the only way to speak

00:10:18.730 --> 00:10:21.430
